      <summary>Why is Motorola Solutions valued so highly by the market?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">MSI is arguably the most dominant monopoly in public safety communications (LMR networks). Their hardware and software are mission-critical, deeply embedded, and extremely difficult to rip-and-replace. Investors pay a premium for this near-utility-like predictability and their successful pivot into high-margin software.</div>
